name: ATLAS BABYLON
description:
A transformative take on a photo by Indro Muktiono. 

This is my first experiment on generative art. Prompted an AI to generate a painting based on my original night city photo, and then I  animated the result through multi-layered motion techniques to add depth and parallax effects.

Jakarta, October 24, 2021.
 1200× 1800 seamlessly looping MP4.
